            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-process-step" data-step="2">
          <div class="hp-step-dot-wrap"><div class="hp-step-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-pen-ruler"></i></div></div>
          <div class="hp-step-content">
            <div class="hp-step-label">Step 3</div>
            <div class="hp-step-card">
              <h4>Design</h4>
              <p>Create lo-fi designs to outline basic structure, develop hi-fi designs for detailed visual representation, and build interactive prototypes for user testing and feedback.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-process-step" data-step="3">
          <div class="hp-step-dot-wrap"><div class="hp-step-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i></div></div>
          <div class="hp-step-content">
            <div class="hp-step-label">Step 4</div>
            <div class="hp-step-card">
              <h4>Develop, Test, and Deploy</h4>
              <p>Utilizing agile methodologies with iterative development cycles, continuous integration and testing, regular feedback sessions, and seamless deployment practices.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-process-step" data-step="4">
          <div class="hp-step-dot-wrap"><div class="hp-step-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i></div></div>
          <div class="hp-step-content">
            <div class="hp-step-label">Step 5</div>
